comment._content:
A copy of this picture can be found in the archives of Arne Fabrikker held in Bergen Byarkiv. The picture is taken in 1898 and the musicians in front are members of Arne Musikkforening. Their names are from left to right:
Lars Rønhovde, John Hansen, Ole Rønhovde, Ingebrigt Hansen, Eirik Brudvik, Ole J.Blindheim, Nils Vik, Ole Hamre og Alboys Frantzen. Arne Musikkforening celebreated 130 years in 2007.
